        "name": "Anchored in Silk",
        "subtype": "ability",
        "text": "The cocoon is incapable of movement beyond slight wriggling in place. It has no Speed and can't move or be moved, even through means such as teleportation, as the Weaver's threads tether it in place physically and astrally. The cocoon casts any spells psychically, substituting verbal and somatic components for expressions of pure unbridled will and removing the manipulate trait from its Cast a Spell action.",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
